  "content": {
    "problemStatement": "What will be the output of the below C code?\n\n```c\n#include\n\nint main() {\n    int num = 0;\n\n    while (num < 10) {\n        num++;\n\n        if (num % 2 == 0) {\n            continue;\n        }\n\n        printf(\"Odd number: %d\\n\", num);\n    }\n\n    return 0;\n}\n```",
